com.here.sdk.gestures

Class Gestures

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.NativeBase
      • com.here.sdk.gestures.Gestures

  • public final class Gestures
extends NativeBase

    Use this class to process touch events from the platform and detect gesture induced actions on the map view. Please note that this class holds strong references to the gesture listeners.
